Spa Baltic Sea - how to scrub your face with hails.

The last week of April.
Previous week was rocking temperatures on 20°C, the following week was hitting 25°C. We got the awesome 5°C, hailstorms and one cold morning of snowfall. So yeah. April is a cruel month.

First time sailing on a German lake.

3706nm of sailing. From Tenerife to Mindelo to Barbados to Tobago Cays to St.Lucia to Martinique. An absolutely fabulous month of my life.

The voyage across the Atlantic

Sailing across the Atlantic

I had sailed on Helena once before, on a weekend trip in the Turku archipelago. But crossing the Atlantic would be a more interesting adventure. For a month this two-masted tall ship would be our home on the ocean.
